dc_title_s: Maryland Legislative Districts: Prince George's County, Maryland, 2014
dc_description_s: State Legislative Districts in Prince George's County This coverage represents the boundaries of the state legislative districts, based on the election cycle the adopted districts are to be used for. While this coverage is maintained by the Prince George's County GIS Section, the boundaries are defined and their representation approved by the Board of Elections. The district boundaries were adopted by the Maryland State Legislature on February 24, 2012.
